---

## Quality Standards (Auto-Enforced)

### Pre-Commit
- TypeScript strict mode (no errors)
- ESLint passes (no errors)
- No console.logs in production
- No TODO comments in prod code

### Pre-Deploy
- All pages load without errors
- Forms submit successfully
- Mobile responsive (test on phone)
- Performance score > 90 (Lighthouse)
- No broken links

**Auto-deploy if all checks pass. No manual approval needed.**

---

## Non-Negotiables (From Sumanth)

**Never:**
- Use Pages Router (App Router only)
- Store API keys in client code
- Skip TypeScript strict mode
- Ship without testing forms
- Deploy broken pages

**Always:**
- Functional components with hooks
- Early returns for error handling
- Mobile-first design
- Accessibility (WCAG AA minimum)
- Sequential learning enforcement (when building academy)

