## Development Workflow

1. Create component/page
2. Test locally (npm run dev)
3. Commit with clear message
4. Push to git (auto-deploys to Vercel staging)
5. Test on staging
6. Merge to main (deploys to production)

**No manual approvals. Just ship.**

